> npx create-react-app project-name

>Create react app - done
>Routing(With params, with queryparams, Authenticated routes(pending...), Nav Active routes, button click navigate to new page) - done
>State(useState) - done
>Parent to child - done
>Forms
>useEffect(Mounting, updating, and unmounting)
>APIs(Axios- get, post put, delete)
>Redux

go to projhect folder and run the code using 
>npm start


